1
00:00:01,630 --> 00:00:04,300
I'll get straight to the point.

2
00:00:04,300 --> 00:00:07,010
What's your relationship with Motomiya?

3
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:09,340
We're college classmates.

4
00:00:09,680 --> 00:00:11,720
During the school festival, I helped Makoto...

5
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:13,990
I did Motomiya-kun's makeup...

6
00:00:13,990 --> 00:00:15,930
Haha.

7
00:00:15,930 --> 00:00:18,270
I don't care about that.

8
00:00:18,270 --> 00:00:20,560
I'm asking if you two are dating.

9
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:23,940
Of course not. What are you talking about?

10
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:26,440
Look...

11
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:28,360
Morimoto-san.

12
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,410
With all due respect...

13
00:00:30,410 --> 00:00:32,740
please don't underestimate me.

14
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:35,580
What do you mean by that?

15
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:37,450
I mean, I can tell.

16
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:40,580
My job is to protect my talent...

17
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:43,460
To protect Motomiya Makoto.

18
00:00:43,710 --> 00:00:45,170
To protect him from any harm.

19
00:00:45,460 --> 00:00:46,550
So do I.

20
00:00:46,550 --> 00:00:48,210
Then please break up with him.

21
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:50,050
What is that supposed to mean?

22
00:00:50,130 --> 00:00:53,090
He's at a critical point in his career.

23
00:00:54,260 --> 00:00:56,180
If your relationship gets out,

24
00:00:56,720 --> 00:00:58,390
he could lose everything.

25
00:01:00,770 --> 00:01:03,610
If you really care about him,

26
00:01:03,730 --> 00:01:06,150
and about his future,

27
00:01:06,940 --> 00:01:09,110
you should understand, right?

28
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:11,820
What about Makoto...?

29
00:01:12,490 --> 00:01:13,780
What did he say?

30
00:01:13,780 --> 00:01:16,370
He listened to my advice, too.

31
00:01:18,410 --> 00:01:20,040
That's all I have to say.

32
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:22,460
I'm counting on you.
